:INFO
Woods to Avoid
Pine contains resin pockets that flare unpredictably under heat and produce heavy smoke. \
Plywood with MDF core or unknown glue types may release toxic fumes when burned. \
Driftwood and reclaimed wood may contain salt, paint, or treatments that are

