3 to 5 Minutes
Time to let a freshly sanded surface settle before starting to burn

:NOTE
Sealing and Finishing After Burning
Leave burned pieces unfinished if display only. \
For functional items or pieces that will be handled, apply a thin coat of food-safe \
mineral oil, beeswax finish, or a water-based varnish after burning is complete. \
Oil finishes darken the wood and deepen the contrast between burned and unburned areas. \
Apply finish sparingly and buff after drying to avoid a plastic look.
